	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_69162">I don't think you can compare mod_perl and Rack (both Rails and Merb are based on Rack these days btw.).
Rack is all about running your code on different HTTP servers using a unified api, while mod_perl gives you the power to hook into the guts of Apache and change low level logic.</div>
		
	
	</div>
